data.description:
Multiple offers as of 12/29
Your new home for the Holidays, start the new year right! Discover this exquisite try-level residence in great condition, HVAC 2018! Water heater less than a year old. Conveniently located just beyond the Hoke County line. Proximity to Fort Liberty (formerly Fort Bragg) adds to the appeal of this property, featuring 4 bedrooms, 3 baths, and double master suites—one on each level. Enjoy effortless access to amenities from this strategically positioned home. Owner will only make appraisal repairs. Please be aware that the owner has recently signed an easement related to a nearby road construction project; we advise conducting thorough Due Diligence. For a seamless closing experience, the preferred choice is McGeachy Hudson and Zuravel.
